desc_short	-----								Serious Sam is a high-adrenaline arcade-action shooter heavily focused on frantic arcade-style action. In a world where cyberpunk meets fantasy-fiction and advanced technology is mixed with black magic and psycho-powers, Sam travels through four beautiful worlds, confronting countless of Mental's minions on his way to Mental's base.							
developer									Croteam					,			Alligator Pit								
